Package se.arkalix.dto.binary

Class ByteArrayReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.arkalix.dto.binary.ByteArrayReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BinaryReader
    public class ByteArrayReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements BinaryReader
    A BinaryReader that reads from a plain byte array.

    This reader is naive in the sense that it does not check for range errors before executing on any contained byte array. However, as range errors are checked by Java on byte array operations, the error messages should still be quite informative for most categories of errors.
